column3: Reset the dock to default i.e. on bottom with autohide disabled.

column2: defaults write com.apple.dock autohide-delay -float 0; defaults write com.apple.dock autohide-time-modifier -float 0.5; killall Dock
column3: Enable quick dock showing with disabled animations.

column2: defaults write com.apple.dock orientation -string left; killall Dock
column3: Places the dock on the left side of the screen.

column2: defaults write com.apple.dock orientation -string right; killall Dock
column3: Places the dock on the right side of the screen.

column2: defaults write com.apple.dock orientation -string bottom; killall Dock
column3: Places the dock on the bottom of the screen.

column2: defaults write com.apple.dock autohide -boolean true; killall Dock
defaults write com.apple.dock autohide -boolean false; killall Dock
